counterpart would cover filateral issues as well as the conflict
in the Democratic Republic of Congo and Guinea Bissau.
</P>
<P>
Nigeria has played a major role in west African peace-keeping
operations, more recently in Liberia and Sierra Leone.
</P>
<P>
Abubakar's visit is regarded as another step to the on-going
mending relations between South Africa and Nigeria, two
influential powers in southern and western Africa respectively.
</P>
<P>
Mbeki visited Nigeria on July 9 this year.
</P>
<P>
Bilateral relations between the two nations had been strained
since 1995 when Mandela led the call for international sanctions
against Nigeria following the execution of several activists in
the country. 
