<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, August 22 (Xinhua) -- South Africa's hopes of
negotiating a peaceful solution to the crisis in Democratic Congo
(DRC) were dashed Saturday when neither DRC President Laurent
Kabila nor his representative arrived in South Africa.
</P>
<P>
