<HEADLINE> Congolese Ministers Represent Kabila in Pretoria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, August 22 (Xinhua) -- President Laurent Kabila sen:W
his justice and his transport ministers to Pretoria Saturday for
