<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Foreign Minister
Sartaj Aziz denied Saturday that U.S. President Bill Clinton
talked to Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif on phone about the attack in
Afghanistan.
</P>
