poem to China next year as a special tribute to the poet, whose
200th birthday falls on June 6, 1999.
</P>
<P>
The average age of members of this ballet troupe named after
Pushkin is 22, the youngest in Russia. Among its members, two are
Labor Red Flag Medal winners, eight are Merited Artists, and five
are winners in domestic or international competitions. 
