<TEXT>
<P>
BUDAPEST, August 21 (Xinhua) -- Welshman Iwan Thomas and Scot
Doug Walker gave Britain double golds here at the European
Athletics Championships on Friday as they captured the men's 400
meters and 200 meters title respectively.
</P>
