In women's 400m, Grit Breuer of Germany finished course in
49.93, well ahead of 33-year-old Czech veteran Helena Fuchsova's
50.21 and Russia's world student games silver medallist Olga
Kotlyarova's 50.38.
</P>
<P>
In men's high jump, Artur Partyka of Poland cleared the 2.34
meters bar to beat Britain's Dalton Grant for the title. 
