Patrick Vieira completed a signing of a new six-year deal with
Arsenal on Friday.
</P>
<P>
After signing the contract, Vieira promised he would try his
best to keep a good relationship with referees.
</P>
<P>
Since joining the London club from AC Milan for 3.5 million
pounds (5.71 million U.S. dollars) two years ago, the combative
22-year-old has suffered at the hands of English referees.
</P>
<P>
